s%20signal%20was%20cut%20off%20after%20about%2015%20minutes.%20Manrique%20said%20some%20of%20the%20assailants%20ran%20from%20the%20studio%20and%20tried%20to%20hide%20when%20they%20realized%20they%20were%20surrounded%20by%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20still%20in%20shock%26quot%3B%20Manrique%20told%20The%20Associated%20Press%20in%20a%20phone%20interview.%20%26quot%3BEverything%20has%20collapsed%20....%20All%20I%20know%20is%20that%20it's%20time%20to%20leave%20this%20country%20and%20go%20very%20far%20away.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEcuador%20has%20been%20rocked%20by%20a%20series%20of%20attacks%2C%20including%20the%20abductions%20of%20several%20police%20officers%2C%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20a%20notorious%20gang%20leader's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fecuador-gang-leader-prison-violence-los-choneros-1bef48cc79d52a854a63a2f3c64ca4b5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eapparent%20weekend%20escape%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fecuador-daniel-noboa-president-bananas-crime-3a75d25860961bc690f8a52536dcf19a%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPresident%20Daniel%20Noboa%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday%20declared%20a%20national%20state%20of%20emergency%2C%20a%20measure%20that%20lets%20authorities%20suspend%20people's%20rights%20and%20mobilize%20the%20military%20in%20places%20like%20prisons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2024%2F01%2F09%2Famericas%2Farmed-men-interrupt-live-tv-ecuador-intl%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20CNN%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20state%20of%20emergency%20will%20last%2060%20days%20as%20police%20look%20to%20clamp%20down%20on%20the%20situation%20and%20will%20include%20curfews%20and%20restrictions%20on%20public%20gatherings%20that%20authorities%20may%20determine%20could%20lead%20to%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20the%20gunmen%20stormed%20the%20TV%20station%2C%20Noboa%20issued%20another%20decree%20designating%2020%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fecuador-bananas-cocaine-europe-drug-trafficking-6d6529e2b1d8f3cbd16aea74ade0b93d%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrug%20trafficking%20gangs%3C%2Fa%3E%20operating%20in%20the%20country%20as%20terrorist%20groups%20and%20authorizing%20Ecuador's%20military%20to%20%26quot%3Bneutralize%26quot%3B%20them%20within%20the%20bounds%20of%20international%20humanitarian%20law.%20It%20also%20said%20the%20country%20had%20entered%20an%20internal%20armed%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEcuador's%20attorney%20general's%20office%20said%20the%2013%20people%20arrested%20will%20be%20charged%20with%20terrorism.%20It%20tweeted%20that%20it%20will%20present%20the%20charges%20in%20coming%20hours.%20Ecuadorian%20law%20establishes%20a%20penalty%20of%20up%20to%2013%20years%20in%20prison%20for%20anyone%20convicted%20of%20terrorism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20not%20said%20how%20many%20attacks%20have%20taken%20place%20since%20authorities%20announced%20that%20Los%20Choneros%20gang%20leader%20Adolfo%20Mac%C3%ADas%2C%20alias%20%26quot%3BFito%2C%26quot%3B%20was%20discovered%20missing%20from%20his%20cell%20in%20a%20low-security%20prison%20Sunday.%20He%20was%20scheduled%20to%20be%20transferred%20to%20a%20maximum%20security%20facility%20that%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Ecuadorean%20officials%20announced%20that%20another%20gang%20leader%2C%20Fabricio%20Col%C3%B3n%20Pico%20of%20the%20Los%20Lobos%20group%2C%20had%20escaped%20from%20a%20prison%20in%20the%20town%20of%20Riobamba.%20Col%C3%B3n%20Pico%20was%20captured%20on%20Friday%20as%20part%20of%20a%20kidnapping%20investigation%20and%20has%20also%20been%20accused%20of%20trying%20to%20murder%20one%20of%20the%20nation's%20lead%20prosecutors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20attacks%20have%20included%20an%20explosion%20near%20the%20house%20of%20the%20president%20of%20the%20National%20Justice%20Court%20and%20the%20Monday%20night%20kidnappings%20of%20four%20police%20officers.%20Police%20said%20one%20officer%20was%20abducted%20in%20the%20capital%2C%20Quito%2C%20and%20three%20in%20Quevedo%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20of%20the%20senior%20intelligence%20officials%20who%20spoke%20with%20the%20Post%20said%20that%20the%20continuous%20attacks%20appear%20to%20be%20connected%20and%20arranged%20by%20the%20Los%20Lobos%20gang%20to%20send%20some%20sort%20of%20message%20to%20the%20country's%20leadership%20%E2%80%94%20although%20what%20that%20message%20is%20has%20not%20been%20clarified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWill%20Freeman%2C%20a%20political%20analyst%20at%20the%20Council%20on%20Foreign%20Relations%2C%20said%20that%20while%20gangs%20in%20Ecuador%20have%20previously%20assassinated%20a%20presidential%20candidate%20and%20set%20off%20car%20bombs%20in%20front%20of%20government%20buildings%2C%20Tuesday's%20events%20marked%20a%20new%20peak%20in%20violence%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20turning%20point%2C%26quot%3B%20Freeman%20said.%20%26quot%3BDepending%20on%20how%20the%20government%20responds%20it%20will%20set%20the%20precedent%20for%20these%20kinds%20of%20incidents%20to%20continue%2C%20or%20it%20will%20use%20this%20as%20a%20catalyst%20and%20make%20some%20very%20necessary%20structural%20reforms%20so%20that%20the%20state%20can%20start%20to%20win%20its%20war%20against%20crime.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELocated%20on%20South%20America's%20Pacific%20coast%20between%20Peru%20and%20Colombia%2C%20the%20world's%20largest%20cocaine%20producers%2C%20Ecuador%20has%20become%20a%20key%20transit%20point%20for%20the%20drug%20in%20recent%20years.%20Much%20of%20the%20violence%20suffered%20by%20the%20country%20comes%20as%20drug%20gangs%20fight%20each%20other%20and%20the%20government%20for%20control%20of%20ports%20and%20smuggling%20routes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFreeman%20said%20that%20Ecuador's%20government%20will%20have%20to%20find%20ways%20to%20control%20prisons%2C%20from%20where%20gang%20leaders%20continue%20to%20lead%20their%20operat