%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Maldives%20Had%20Begun%20Talks%20of%20Visit%20to%20India%20Soon%20After%20President%20Mohamed%20Muizzu's%20Inauguration%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F10083423%2FF4XY5QwaMAAWU72.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Maldives%20had%20proposed%20a%20visit%20of%20President%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%20to%20India%20immediately%20after%20he%20took%20over%20office%20in%20November%20last.%20But%2C%20with%20Muizzu%20having%20chosen%20Turkey%20as%20first%20destination%20and%20thanks%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20is%20currently%20on%20a%20China%20trip%2C%20an%20India%20visit%20does%20not%20seem%20to%20be%20scheduled%20in%20the%20near%20future.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuizzu%20had%20won%20the%20presidential%20elections%20last%20year%2C%20targeting%20the%20incumbent%20Ibrahim%20Solih%20for%20endangering%20Maldives%E2%80%99%20sovereignty%20by%20fostering%20close%20military%20ties%20with%20India.%20The%20opposition%20had%20campaign%20on%20an%20%E2%80%98India%20Out%E2%80%99%20platform%20to%20oust%20alleged%20Indian%20military%20personnel%20from%20the%20island%20nation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20day%20after%20being%20sworn%20in%2C%20Muizzu%20had%20formally%20requested%20India%20to%20withdraw%20its%20troops%20stationed%20in%20the%20Maldives.%20These%20troops%20operate%20two%20helicopters%20and%20a%20Dornier%20aircraft%20for%20humanitarian%20purposes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESoon%20after%2C%20the%20new%20Maldivian%20government%20also%20conveyed%20to%20the%20Indian%20high%20commission%20that%20President%20Muizzu%20would%20like%20to%20visit%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20as%20both%20sides%20were%20considering%20dates%2C%20the%20Maldives%20president%E2%80%99s%20office%20announced%20that%20he%20would%20be%20travelling%20to%20Turkey%2C%20breaking%20a%