ts%20position%20as%20the%20main%20destination%20for%20tourists%20to%20the%20Indian%20ocean%20island%20nation.%20%E2%80%9CChina%20was%20our%20number%20one%20market%20pre-COVID%2C%20and%20it%20is%20my%20request%20that%20we%20intensify%20efforts%20for%20China%20to%20regain%20this%20position%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpresidency.gov.mv%2FPress%2FArticle%2F29584%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuizzu%E2%80%99s%20comments%20were%20significant%20amidst%20escalating%20tensions%20between%20the%20two%20nations%2C%20triggered%20by%20derogatory%20statements%20from%20Maldivian%20ministers%20regarding%20the%20Indian%20PM%E2%80%99s%20visit%20to%20the%20Lakshadweep%20islands.%20The%20three%20deputy%20ministers%20were%20subsequently%20%E2%80%9Csuspended%E2%80%9D%20by%20Maldives.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFollowing%20the%20tweets%2C%20there%20was%20outrage%20in%20the%20Indian%20social%20media%2C%20with%20some%20users%20advocating%20for%20a%20boycotting%20any%20travel%20to%20Maldives.%20Over%20the%20past%20two%20days%2C%20numerous%20Indian%20celebrities%2C%20including%20film%20stars%2C%20simultaneously%20announced%20on%20X%20that%20they%20would%20opt%20for%20an%20Indian%20destination%20instead%20of%20choosing%20Maldives.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20In%202023%2C%20India%20had%20narrowly%20surpassed%20Russia%20to%20become%20the%20primary%20source%20of%20foreign%20tourists%20for%20Maldives.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704856091000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F10083423%2FF4XY5QwaMAAWU72.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fmaldives-mohamed-muizzu-india-china-turkey-visit%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Possibilities%20of%20a%20visit%20by%20the%20new%20president%20look%20increasingly%20unlikely%20in%20the%20near%20future.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fmaldives-mohamed-muizzu-india-china-turkey-visit%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gunmen%20storm%20TV%20studio%3A%20Ecuador%20erupts%20in%20'civil%20war'%20with%20cartel%20thugs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704856013000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106682567%2Cimgsize-300558.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fon-air-take-over-of-tv-studio-by-gunmen-ecuador-erupts-in-civil-war-with-cartel-thugs%2Farticleshow%2F106681770.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20shocking%20turn%20of%20events%2C%2013%20gunmen%20took%20over%20the%20TC%20television%20station%20in%20Guayaquil%20during%20a%20live%20broadcast.%20The%20assailants%2C%20clad%20in%20balaclavas%20and%20mostly%20dressed%20in%20black%2C%20brandished%20guns%20and%20accosted%20staff%20members.%20The%20chaos%2C%20which%20included%20gunshots%20and%20yelling%2C%20was%20broadcast%20live%20for%20about%2020%20minutes.%20At%20least%2010%20people%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20violence%20linked%20to%20criminal%20gangs%20in%20Ecuador.%20At%20least%20seven%20police%20officers%20were%20kidnapped%20in%20separate%20incidents%20in%20Machala%2C%20Quito%2C%20and%20Los%20Rios%20province.%20President%20Noboa%20declared%20a%2060-day%20state%20of%20emergency%20on%20Monday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20WORLD%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20Permission%20Yet%20For%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20Yatra%20In%20Manipur%20After%20Fresh%20Violence%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFresh%20violence%20in%20the%20border%20town%20of%20Moreh%20in%20Manipur%20has%20cast%20a%20shadow%20over%20the%20'Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%2C'%20a%20nationwide%20march%20planned%20by%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20as%20the%20state%20government%20is%20yet%20to%20grant%20permission%20for%20the%20event.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20in%20Moreh%20remains%20critical%2C%20marked%20by%20a%20recent%20exchange%20of%20gunfire%20between%20Manipur%20police%20and%20militants%20along%20the%20Indo-Myanmar%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur%20Chief%20Minister%20Biren%20Singh%20acknowledged%20the%20critical%20state%20of%20affairs%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BMass%20combing%20operations%26quot%3B%20are%20currently%20underway%20by%20a%20joint%20effort%20of%20Assam%20Rifles%2C%20BSF%2C%20and%20state%20police%20to%20apprehend%20armed%20personnel%20responsible%20for%20the%20attacks%20on%20security%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Rahul%20Gandhi-led%20'Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra'%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BGiving%20permission%20to%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20rally%20is%20under%20active%20consideration.%20We%20are%20taking%20reports%20from%20various%20security%20agencies.%20After%20receiving%20reports%20from%20them%2C%20we%20will%20take%20a%20concrete%20decision%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20responding%20to%20a%20question%20from%20reporters%20regarding%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20exchange%20of%20fire%20in%20Moreh%20occurred%20Monday%20morning%20when%20militants%20targeted%20security%20forces%20in%20certain%20parts%20of%20the%20town.%20Officials%20reported%20the%20use%20of%20mortar%20shells%20during%20the%20attack%2C%20though%20no%20casualties%20were%20reported%20on%20either%20side.%20This%20follows%20a%20series%20of%20incidents%2C%20including%20firing%20and%20bomb%20attacks%20in%20Ward%207%20and%20Moreh%20Bazar%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20party%2C%20led%20by%20national%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20aims%20to%20launch%20the%20'Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra'%20on%20January%2014%20from%20Hatta%20Kangjeibung%20in%20the%20Imphal%20East%20district.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20Guwahati%2C%20Congress%20general%20secretary%20K