ng%3D%5C%22es%5C%22%3EQue%20pena%20todo%20lo%20que%20esta%20pasando%20con%20los%20hermanos%20del%20canal%20tc%20televisi%C3%B3n%2C%20Dios%20los%20cuide%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FbehRNVacSz%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FbehRNVacSz%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Emergencias%20Ec%20(%40EmergenciasEc)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEmergenciasEc%2Fstatus%2F1744805395749609668%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%209%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELong%20a%20peaceful%20haven%20sandwiched%20between%20top%20cocaine%20exporters%20Colombia%20and%20Peru%2C%20Ecuador%20has%20seen%20violence%20explode%20in%20recent%20years%20as%20enemy%20gangs%20with%20links%20to%20Mexican%20and%20Colombian%20cartels%20vie%20for%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20ordered%20the%20armed%20forces%20to%20carry%20out%20military%20operations%20to%20neutralize%20these%20groups%2C%26quot%3B%20Noboa%20wrote%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20comments%20came%20shortly%20after%20attackers%20carrying%20rifles%20and%20grenades%20stormed%20the%20studio%20of%20TC%20television%20in%20the%20port%20city%20of%20Guayaquil%20as%20a%20woman%20was%20heard%20amid%20gunshots%20pleading%3A%20%26quot%3BDon't%20shoot%2C%20please%20don't%20shoot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20intruders%20forced%20terrified%20crew%20onto%20the%20ground%2C%20and%20a%20person%20could%20be%20heard%20screaming%20in%20apparent%20pain%20as%20the%20studio%20lights%20went%20off%2C%20but%20the%20live%20broadcast%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlease%2C%20they%20came%20in%20to%20kill%20us.%20God%20don't%20let%20this%20happen.%20The%20criminals%20are%20on%20air%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20TC%20employee%20told%20AFP%20in%20a%20WhatsApp%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20about%2030%20minutes%20of%20chaos%2C%20officers%20were%20seen%20entering%20the%20studio%20while%20someone%20then%20called%20out%20that%20they%20%26quot%3Bhave%20a%20wounded%20companion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20Tuesday%2C%20gangsters%20kidnapped%20police%20officers%20and%20set%20off%20explosives%20in%20several%20cities%20in%20response%20to%20a%2060-day%20state%20of%20emergency%20and%20nighttime%20curfew%20declared%20by%20Noboa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20'You%20will%20get%20war'%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoboa%2C%2036%2C%20was%20elected%20in%20October%20on%20a%20pledge%20to%20fight%20rampant%20drug-related%20crime%20and%20violence%20in%20the%20South%20American%20country%20--%20once%20considered%20a%20bastion%20of%20peace%2C%20but%20now%20a%20key%20stop%20on%20the%20US-%20and%20Europe-bound%20cocaine%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20vowed%20Monday%20to%20bring%20the%20fight%20to%20the%20cartels%20after%20a%20powerful%20gang%20leader%2C%20Jose%20Adolfo%20Macias%2C%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BFito%2C%26quot%3B%20escaped%20from%20prison%20the%20previous%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20gangs%20hit%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20reported%20multiple%20explosions%20and%20said%20seven%20police%20officers%20had%20been%20kidnapped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20chilling%20video%20circulating%20on%20social%20media%20showed%20three%20of%20the%20kidnapped%20officers%20sitting%20on%20the%20ground%20with%20a%20gun%20pointed%20at%20them%20as%20one%20is%20forced%20to%20read%20a%20statement%20addressed%20to%20Noboa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20declared%20war%2C%20you%20will%20get%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20clearly%20terrified%20officer%20reads.%20%26quot%3BYou%20declared%20a%20state%20of%20emergency.%20We%20declare%20police%2C%20civilians%20and%20soldiers%20to%20be%20the%20spoils%20of%20war.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20added%20that%20anyone%20found%20on%20the%20street%20after%2011%3A00%20pm%20(0500%20GMT)%20%26quot%3Bwill%20be%20executed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20presidency%20and%20metro%20stations%20in%20Quito%20were%20under%20military%20guard%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20say%20an%20explosive%20device%20was%20thrown%20near%20a%20police%20station%20in%20Esmeraldas%20on%20the%20northwest%20coast%20and%20two%20vehicles%20were%20burned%20in%20other%20areas%2C%20with%20no%20one%20killed%20or%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Quito%2C%20a%20car%20was%20reportedly%20blown%20up%2C%20and%20a%20device%20exploded%20near%20a%20pedestrian%20bridge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20'Return%20peace%20to%20all%20Ecuadorans'%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20manhunt%20is%20under%20way%20for%20Fito%2C%20who%20had%20been%20serving%20a%2034-year%20sentence%20for%20organized%20crime%2C%20drug%20trafficking%20and%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2044-year-old%20leader%20of%20the%20powerful%20Los%20Choneros%20gang%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20escaped%20just%20hours%20before%20police%20arrived%20to%20conduct%20an%20inspection%20of%20the%20Guayaquil%20prison%20where%20he%20was%20held.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20officials%20said%20another%20narco%20boss%20--%20Los%20Lobos%20leader%20Fabricio%20Colon%20Pico%20--%20has%20also%20escaped%20since%20his%20arrest%20last%20Friday%20for%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20a%20plot%20to%20assassinate%20Ecuador's%20attorney%20general.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnrest%20broke%20out%20Monday%20at%20penitentiaries%20in%20six%20of%20Ecuador's%2024%20provinces%2C%20according%20to%20Ecuador's%20prison%20authority%20SNAI%2C%20with%20guards%20taken%20hostage%20at%20some%20of%20the%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeavily%20armed%20police%20and%20soldiers%20entered%20the%20prisons%20of%20El%20Oro%2C%20Loja%2C%20Chimborazo%2C%20Cotopaxi%2C%20Azuay%20and%20Pichincha%2C%20after%20which%20the%20military%20distributed%20images%20of%20half-naked%20inmates%20rounded%20up%20in%20courtyards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SNAI%20has%20not%20revealed%20whether%20the%20guards%20have%20since%20been%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoboa%20said%20the%20uprisings%20appeared%20to%20be%20revenge%20for%20his%20actions%20to%20%26quot%3Bregain%20control%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20country's%20prisons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20he%20vowed%20to%20%26quot%3Bnot%20negotiate%20with%20terrorists%20nor%20rest%20until%20we%20return%20peace%20to%20all%20Ecuadorans.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDrug%20violence%20has%20taken%20a%20heavy%20toll%20on%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20murder%20rate%20quadrupled%20from%202018%20to%202022%2C%20while%20last%20year%20became%20the%20most%20violent%20yet%20with%20more%20than%207%2C800%20homicides%20in%20the%20country%20of%20about%2017%20million%20people%20and%20220%20tons%20of%20drugs%20seized%2C%20a%20new%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20February%202021%2C%20clashes%20between%20prisoners%20have%20left%20more%20than%20460%20dead%2C%20many%20beheaded%20or%20burnt%20alive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704855480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F6t7p134_ecuador-tv-studio-_625x300_10_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fgunshots-on-live-tv-after-ecuador-gangsters-storm-studio-4833217%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ecuadoran%20President%20Daniel%20Noboa%20ordered%20military%20operations%20on%20Tuesday%20against%20the%20country's%20powerful%20criminal%20groups%20after%20hooded%20gunmen%20stormed%20a%20television%20studio%20and%20gangsters%20threatened%20to%20execute%20security%20forces%20and%20civilians.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fgunshots-on-live-tv-after-ecuador-gangsters-storm-studio-4833217%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Musk's%20X%20set%20to%20allow%20users%20to%20make%20payments%20on%20platform%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22publishe