n%20the%20atmosphere%20and%20the%20splendour%20of%20the%20hall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EHeartfelt%20congratulations%20to%20Sheetal%20Devi%20on%20being%20bestowed%20with%20the%20Arjuna%20Award%20for%20her%20extraordinary%20accomplishments%20in%20Para-Archery.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnSheetal%2C%20you%20are%20a%20role%20model%20for%20the%20nation%20and%20the%20world%3B%20you%20have%20made%20the%20world%20acknowledge%20your%20passion%2C%20zeal%2C%20and%20hard%20work.%20May%20you%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F0kOrh4io0Q%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F0kOrh4io0Q%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Anurag%20Thakur%20(%40ianuragthakur)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fianuragthakur%2Fstatus%2F1744625095749021943%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%209%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EMurmu%20then%20walked%20down%20the%20podium%20to%20present%20the%20Arjuna%20to%20wheelchair-bound%20para-canoeist%20Prachi%20Yadav%2C%20winner%20of%20gold%20in%20Hangzhou%2C%20once%20again%20drawing%20a%20huge%20round%20of%20applause.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShami%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20recovering%20from%20an%20ankle%20injury%2C%20was%20there%20to%20receive%20the%20honours%20and%20the%20crowd%20duly%20acknowledged%20his%20achievements%20by%20giving%20him%20and%20his%20art%20the%20pride%20of%20place%20with%20an%20ovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pace%20bowler%20took%2024%20wickets%20in%20seven%20World%20Cup%20games%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20aim%20is%20to%20keep%20myself%20fit%20as%20far%20as%20possible%2C%20as%20the%20next%20two%20tournaments%20and%20series%20are%20big.%20I%20will%20focus%20on%20fitness%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20PTI%20at%20a%20sports%20ministry%20reception%20last%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20receiving%20a%20huge%20round%20of%20applause%20was%20the%2