%20PR%20at%20the%20UNGA%20meeting%20today%20on%20the%20situation%20in%20Middle%20East%2C%20including%20Palestinian%20question%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F41nXLPtPBd%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F41nXLPtPBd%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20India%20at%20UN%2C%20NY%20(%40IndiaUNNewYork)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIndiaUNNewYork%2Fstatus%2F1744866054273441793%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%209%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20General%20Assembly%20(UNGA)%20on%20the%20prevailing%20situation%20in%20West%20Asia%2C%20Ms%20Kamboj%20highlighted%20India's%20continuous%20efforts%20to%20normalise%20the%20ongoing%20situation%20in%20the%20region%20and%20extend%20humanitarian%20aid%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20leadership%20of%20India%20is%20in%20constant%20touch%20with%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20region%2C%20including%20those%20of%20Israel%20and%20Palestine.%20We've%20also%20voiced%20our%20views%20in%20multilateral%20forums%20such%20as%20the%20G20%2C%20the%20BRICS%2C%20and%20at%20the%20Global%20South%20Summit%20in%20November%202023%2C%20and%20we%20have%20reiterated%20our%20longstanding%20and%20principal%20position%20on%20the%20issue.%20We%20have%20also%20called%20for%20continued%20humanitarian%20aid%20for%20the%20affected%20population%20and%20in%20this%20regard%2C%20we%20hope%20that%20Security%20Council%20Resolution%202720%20would%20aid%20in%20enhancing%20humanitarian%20assistance%2C%26quot%3B%20India's%20permanent%20envoy%20to%20the%20UN%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20has%20so%20far%20provided%2070%20tonnes%20of%20humanitarian%20aid%2C%20including%2016.5%20tonnes%20of%20medicine%20and%20medical%20supplies%20in%20two%20tranches%2C%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Palestine.%20We've%20also%20provided%20us%20dollars%205%20million%2C%20including%20the%20USD%202.5%20million%20we%20provided%20in%20end%20December%202023%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%20Relief%20and%20Works%20Agency%20for%20Palestine%20refugees%20in%20the%20Near%20east%2C%20which%20will%20go%20to%20support%20the%20agency's%20core%20programs%20and%20services%2C%20including%20education%2C%20health%20care%2C%20relief%20and%20social%20services%20provided%20to%20Palestinian%20refugees%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Kamboj%20said%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20permanent%20representative%20to%20the%20world%20body%20reiterated%20the%20two-state%20solution%2C%20saying%20that%20a%20peaceful%20resolution%20of%20the%20conflict%20through%20dialogue%20and%20diplomacy%20was%20the%20only%20way%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20message%20that%20India%20has%20conveyed%20since%20the%20start%20of%20this%20conflict%20is%20clear%20and%20consistent.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20prevent%20escalation%2C%20to%20ensure%20continued%20delivery%20of%20humanitarian%20aid%2C%20and%20to%20work%20towards%20an%20early%20restoration%20of%20peace%20and%20stability.%20A%20peaceful%20resolution%20of%20the%20conflict%20through%20dialogue%20and%20diplomacy%20is%20the%20only%20way%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Kamboj%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20reaffirming%20India's%20firm%20commitment%20to%20achieving%20a%20just%2C%20peaceful%20and%20lasting%20solution%20to%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20issue.%20We%20firmly%20believe%20that%20only%20a%20two%20state%20solution%20achieved%20through%20direct%20and%20meaningful%20negotiations%20between%20both%20sides%20on%20final%20status%20issues%2C%20will%20deliver%20an%20enduring%20peace%20that%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%20and%20Palestine%20desire%20and%20deserve.%20For%20this%2C%20we%20urge%20the%20parties%20to%20deescalate%2C%20eschew%20violence%20and%20work%20towards%20creating%20conditions%20for%20an%20early%20resumption%20of%20direct%20peace%20negotiations%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704854280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-03%2Fg83p0ops_ruchira-kamboj_625x300_10_March_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Floss-of-lives-unacceptable-dialogue-only-way-forward-india-on-israel-hamas-war-4833220%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20permanent%20representative%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%2C%20Ruchira%20Kamboj%2C%20strongly%20condemned%20the%20loss%20of%20civilian%20lives%20in%20the%20ongoing%20war%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20saying%20that%20the%20alarming%20humanitarian%20crisis%20was%20'clearly%20unacceptable'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Floss-of-lives-unacceptable-dialogue-only-way-forward-india-on-israel-hamas-war-4833220%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Floss-of-lives-unacceptable-dialogue-only-way-forward-india-on-israel-hamas-war-4833220%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Floss-of-lives-unacceptable-dialogue-only-way-forward-india-on-israel-hamas-war-4833220%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Women%20Who%20Fought%20for%20Justice%20for%20Bilkis%20Bano%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F10080129%2FUntitled-design-11.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20the%20petitioners%20who%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20against%20the%20Gujarat%20government%E2%80%99s%20premature%20release%20of%20the%2011%20convicts%20jailed%20for%20gang-rape%20and%20multiple%20murders%20in%20the%20Bilkis%20Bano%20case%2C%20it%20was%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Independence%20Day%20speech%20in%202022%20that%20proved%20the%20last%20straw.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECelebrating%2075%20years%20of%20Independence%2C%20Modi%20invoked%20woman%20power%20or%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Enari%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Eshakti%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98%20from%20the%20Red%20Fort%20and%20called%20for%20an%20end%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1852024%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cevery%20behaviour%2C%20culture%20that%20humiliates%20and%20demeans%20women.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJust%20then%2C%20the%20convicts%2C%20who%20had%20been%20sentenced%20to%20life%20for%20gang-raping%20a%20pregnant%20Bilkis%20Bano%2C%20members%20of%20her%20family%2C%20and%20also%20murdering%20at%20least%2014%20of%20them%20in%202002%20while%20the%20Gujarat%20riots%20were%20on%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbilkis-bano-husband-convict-release%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewalked%20out%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20Godhra%20sub-jail.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COn%20August%2015%2C%20when%20the%20prime%20minister%20was%20talking%20about%20women%E2%80%99s%20security%20and%20honouring%20women%2C%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20gave%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fbilkis-bano-case-11-men-sentenced-to-life-imprisonment-released-under-gujarat-govts-remission-policy%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20remission%20order%20and%20released%20them%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(the%20convicts).%20I%20then%20heard%20that%20Bilkis%20made%20a%20statement%20saying%20%E2%80%98is%20this%20the%20end%20of%20justice%3F%E2%80%99%20That%20really%20shook%20me%20and%20many%20like%20me%20who%20thought%2C%20%E2%80%98What%20is%20the%20use%20of%20us%20being%20around%3F%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20CPI(M)%20leader%20and%20activist%20Subhashini%20Ali%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAli%2C%20former%20professor%20Roop%20Rekha%20Verma%20and%20journalist%20Revati%20Laul%20jointly%20filed%20a%20petition%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20challenging%20the%20Gujarat%20government%E2%80%99s%20remission%20and%20release%20order.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20trying%20to%20think%20of%20what%20we%20could%20do%20and%20it%20was%20very%20fortunate%20that%20lawyers%20like%20Kapil%20Sibal%20and%20Aparna%20Bhatt%20and%20others%20came%20forward%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ali.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20January%208%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fbilkis-bano-supreme-court-gujarat-not-competent-remission%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Equashed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20release%20order%2C%20said%20that%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20did%20not%20have%20the%20power%20to%20grant%20such%20a%20release%20to%20the%20convicts%20and%20directed%20them%20to%20return%20to%20prison%20within%20two%20weeks.%20The%20court%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20had%20%E2%80%9Cacted%20in%20complicity%E2%80%9D%20with%20the%20convicts.%20The%20bench%20of%20Justices%20B.V.%20Nagarathna%20and%20Ujjwal%20Bhuyan%20also%20held%20that%20the%20judgement%20of%20May%2013%2C%202022%2C%20by%20a%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Ajay%20Rastogi%20and%20Vikram%20Nath%2C%20which%20directed%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20to%20consider%20remission%2C%20%E2%80%9Ca%20nullity%E2%80%9D%20as%20it%20was%20obtained%20by%20%E2%80%9Cplaying%20fraud%20on%20the%20court%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Cruel%20joke%20on%20the%20nation%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERoop%20Rekha%20Verma%2C%20former%20professor%20at%20Lucknow%20University%20who%20was%20in%20Delhi%20when%20the%20news%20of%20the%20remission%20orders%20came%20out%20said%20that%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20speech%20was%20%E2%80%9C%20a%20cruel%20joke%20on%20the%20nation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Prime%20Minister%20who%20was%20crying%20about%20violence%20on%20women%20in%20his%20Independence%20Day%20speech%20had%20already%20given%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fconvicts-in-bilkis-bano-case-released-for-good-behaviour-with-mha-approval-gujarat-govt%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epermission%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20remission.%20That%20was%20a%20cruel%20joke%20on%20the%20nation%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVerma%20said%20that%20she%20then%20discussed%20the%20developments%20with%20some%20of%20her%20friends%20and%20associates%2C%20and%20the%20%E2%80%9Cidea%20cropped%20up%20collectively%E2%80%9D%20to%20explore%20legal%20options.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAlthough%20by%20that%20time%20we%20had%20enough%20examples%20to%20not%20look%20at%20courts%20with%20much%20hope%2C%20but%20there%20was%20no%20other%20door%20to%20knock%20on%2C%20apart%20from%20a%20petition%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJournalist%20Revati%20Laul%20came%20onboard%20to%20become%20a%20petitioner%20in%20the%20case%20when%20she%20was%20told%20that%20they%20were%20looking%20for%20a%20third%20woman%20petitioner.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20looking%20for%20a%20third%20woman%20petitioner%20who%20had%20some%20%3Cem%3Elocus%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Estandi%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20the%20matter.%20I%20was%20asked%20if%20I%20would%20like%20to%20be%20the%20third%20petitioner.%20I%20had%20written%20the%20book%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAnatomy%20of%20Hate%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20which%20is%20based%20on%20the%20Gujarat%20riots%20and%20have%20been%20based%20in%20Gujarat%20for%20a%20while%20during%20and%20after%20the%20riots.%20I%20feel%20strongly%20about%20this%20case%20and%20I%20agreed%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20petitioners%20said%20that%20after%20they%20filed%20their%20petition%2C%20they%20found%20out%20that%20another%20PIL%20had%20been%20filed%20by%20now%20expelled%20Trinamool%20Congress%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra%20through%20lawyer%20Indira%20Jaising.%20Subsequently%20another%20petition%20was%20filed%20by%20former%20IPS%20officer%20Meeran%20Chadha%20Borwankar%20in%20September%202022.%20Her%20group%20also%20included%20petitioners%20Jagdeep%20Chokhar%20and%20Madhu%20Bhandari.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBorwankar%20said%20that%20she%20decided%20to%20%E2%80%9Cstep%20in%E2%80%9D%20and%20file%20a%20case%20when%20she%20realised%20that%20Bano%20herself%20had%20not%20challenged%20the%20remission%20orders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20following%20the%20case%20closely%20and%20decided%20to%20step%20in%20when%20I%20realised%20that%20Bilkis%20Bano%20had%20not%20challenged%20the%20remission%20orders.%20But%20she%20did%20so%20later%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Why%20should%20Bilkis%20have%20to%20come%20up%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBano%20moved%20the%20apex%20court%20against%20the%20remission%20orders%20only%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fbilkis-bano-supreme-court-release-gangrape-convicts-8297993%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENovember%2C%202022%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20following%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20one%20of%20the%20convicts%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fbilkis-bano-case-convict-questions-maintainability-pleas-challenge-remission%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Equestioning%20the%20maintainability%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20these%20petitions%20saying%20the%20petitioners%20have%20no%20locus%20standi%20and%20are%20%E2%80%9Ccomplete%20strangers%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eher%20lawyer%20for%20the%20past%20two%20decades%2C%20Shobha%20Gupta%20said%20that%20Bano%20had%20to%20become%20a%20petitioner%20after%20the%20maintainability%20of%20these%20petitions%20were%20challenged%20in%20court.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20personally%20very%20clear%2C%20%E2%80%98Why%20should%20she%20alone%20have%20to%20come%20up%3F%E2%80%99%20It%20was%20not%20an%20individual%20crime.%20It%20was%20a%20crime%20against%20humanity%20and%20a%20barbaric%20nature%20of%20crime.%20It%20is%20for%20the%20society%20to%20decide.%20That%20is%20why%20she%20did%20not%20take%20the%20plunge%20to%20begin%20with%20and%20I%20am%20glad%20she%20took%20her%20time%20to%20decide.%20In%20the%20meantime%20the%20right%20spirited%20persons%20challenged%20(the%20remission%20order)%20within%20no%20time%20and%20the%20court%20issued%20a%20notice%20in%20the%20PIL%20petitions%20on%20August%2025%20(2022).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGupta%20said%20that%20the%20remission%20orders%20had%20come%20as%20%E2%80%9Crude%20shock%E2%80%9D%20to%20Bano.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CNobody%20could%20think%20this%20could%20happen%20so%20secretively.%20Suddenly%20you%20find%20that%20your%20rapists%20are%20roaming%20around%20being%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fbilkis-bano-rape-case-convicts-greeted-garlands-vhp-office-1988996-2022-08-17%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehonoured%20and%20felicitated%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20immediate%20reaction%20was%20that%20this%20was%20wrong.%20It%20has%20to%20be%20objected%20to%20but%20it%20is%20always%20tough%20to%20restart%20it%20(the%20fight)%20and%20how%20many%20times%20and%20for%20how%20long%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Milestone%20on%20the%20road%20to%20justice%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%2011%20convicts%20now%20being%20directed%20by%20the%20court%20to%20return%20to%20jail%2C%20Jaising%20who%20represented%20Moitra%20said%20that%20the%20judgement%20was%20extraordinary%20as%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20rarely%20declares%20its%20own%20judgement%20as%20null%20and%20void.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20also%20gives%20you%20a%20roadmap%20to%20justice.%20I%20know%20they%20will%20apply%20to%20Maharashtra.%20We%20have%20to%20wait%20and%20see%20what%20happens%20in%20the%20future%20but%20the%20judgement%20is%20a%20milestone%20on%20the%20journey%20to%20justice%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20Verma%2C%20the%20judgement%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20faith%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20been%20low.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20verdict%20is%20precious%20to%20me%20in%20many%20ways.%20When%20our%20faith%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20other%20courts%20was%20sagging%20low%20at%20that%20time%20such%20a%20judgement%20uplifts%20our%20faith%20in%20courts%20at%20least%20partially.%20It%20means%20to%20me%20not%20only%20individually%20but%20to%20the%20country%20as%20well%20that%20when%20judges%20are%20under%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%2C%20a%20judgement%20can%20come%20that%20goes%20strictly%20by%20law%20but%20also%20puts%20some%20governments%20in%20the%20dock%20and%20says%20plainly%20that%20the%20state%20was%20hand%20in%20glove%20in%20complicity%20with%20the%20criminals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fchandrachud-orator-courtroom-judgments-babri-ayodhya%5C%22%3EThe%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20Phenomenon%3A%20Creativity%20in%20the%20Courtroom%2C%20Stirring%20Rhetoric%20Outside%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20shows%20that%20there%20are%20a%20few%20judges%20who%20don%E2%80%99t%20serve%20as%20the%20staff%20of%20the%20government%20but%20will%20do%20what%20is%20expected%20of%20them%20and%20this%20expectation%20being%20fulfilled%20means%20everything%20in%20a%20democracy%20that%20we%20have%20a%20door%20to%20knock%20on%20and%20we%20will%20get%20justice%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELaul%20said%20that%20the%20judgement%20comes%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cclear%20streak%20of%20light%E2%80%9D%20in%20dark%20times.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20(judgement)%20is%20a%20very%20clear%20streak%20of%20light.%20We%20must%20always%20use%20this%20streak%20of%20light%20to%20undo%20the%20dark%20and%20that%20requires%20a%20lot%20of%20work.%20We%20need%20to%20break%20the%20word%20Bilkis%20down%20and%20we%20as%20citizens%20need%20to%20ask%20ourselves%20%E2%80%93%20what%20is%20the%20institutional%20failure%20that%20allowed%20Bilkis%E2%80%99s%20rape%20to%20become%20a%20public%20performance%3F%20What%20have%20we%20done%20as%20citizens%20to%20allow%20this%20monstrosity%3F%20It%20is%20not%20the%20optics%20but%20it%20is%20about%20what%20you%20and%20I%20are%20doing%20everyday%20that%20enables%20or%20disables%20this.%20We%20should%20not%20stop%20asking%20ourselves%20this%20question%20because%20otherwise%20we%20will%20be%20reducing%20this%20very%20important%20day%20to%20a%20pantomime%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAli%20said%20that%20the%20larger%20message%20behind%20this%20judgement%20is%20to%20look%20beyond%20this%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwomen%E2%80%99s%20issue.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CPlease%20do%20not%20think%20of%20this%20as%20a%20woman%E2%80%99s%20fight.%20It%20is%20a%20fight%20to%20save%20this%20country%20from%20gross%20injustice%20and%20the%20Constitution%20being%20replaced%20by%20%3Cem%3EManusmriti%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20every%20which%20way%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBorwankar%20said%20that%20while%20it%20took%20a%20group%20of%20largely%20women%20to%20bring%20justice%20to%20Bano%2C%20the%20judgement%20shows%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cstate%20cannot%20be%20partisan%20in%20its%20conduct.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Not%20a%20lone%20battle%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20her%20first%20public%20statement%20after%20the%20judgement%20issued%20through%20Gupta%20on%20Monday%2C%20Bano%20said%20that%20she%20can%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ftoday-i-can-breathe-again-says-bilkis-bano-after-landmark-supreme-court-judgement%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cbreathe%20again%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20She%20also%20thanked%20Gupta%20for%20never%20%E2%80%9Callowing%20her%20to%20lose%20faith%20in%20the%20idea%20of%20justice.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGupta%20said%20that%20she%20had%20not%20charged%20a%20penny%20in%20the%20matter%20right%20from%20when%20she%20was%20brought%20in%20by%20the%20National%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%20(NHRC)%20as%20a%20lawyer%20in%20the%20case%20following%20the%20riots%20in%202002.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20have%20the%20capacity%20as%20a%20lawyer%20why%20won%E2%80%99t%20you%20do%20this%20for%20society%3F%20I%20was%20just%20five%20years%20into%20the%20profession.%20I%20was%20told%20by%20the%20NHRC%20that%20we%20have%20enough%20funds%20to%20pay%20lawyers%20but%20I%20said%20no%20not%20in%20this%20matter%20not%20even%20for%20paperwork.%20You%20have%20a%20job%20in%20society.%20It%20is%20something%20for%20the%20society%20you%20have%20to%20do.%20We%20are%20all%20a%20part%20of%20the%20society.%20She%20was%20a%20victim%20who%20was%20a%20direct%20sufferer%20of%20the%20riots.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20each%20one%20of%20us%20suffered%20through%20the%20case.%20Like%20in%20Nirbhaya%20each%20one%20of%20us%20suffered%20as%20we%20witnessed%20it.%20Now%20with%20her%20case%20we%20are%20all%20associated%20because%20we%20have%20all%20seen%20the%20case.%20I%20stood%20by%20her%20because%20we%20want%20to%20tell%20her%20and%20society%20that%20you%20are%20not%20alone%20and%20this%20is%20not%20a%20lone%20battle%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704853998000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F10080129%2FUntitled-design-11.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fthe-women-who-fought-for-justice-for-bilkis-bano%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Behind%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20judgment%20against%20the%20Gujarat%20government's%20premature%20release%20of%20the%2011%20convicts%20charged%20with%20gang-rape%20and%20mass%20murder%20are%20a%20group%20of%20women%20who%20came%20together%20for%20a%20cause%20they%20believed%20in.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fthe-women-who-fought-for-justice-for-bilkis-bano%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jeffrey%20Epstein%20accuser%20says%20in%20deposition%20she%20was%20forced%20to%20have%20sex%20with%20former%20Victoria's%20Secret%20CEO%20Les%20Wexner%20and%20that%20he%20had%20sex%20with%20minors%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222137%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wexner%20with%20hand%20up%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659dc38adcdb354a98561518%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221449%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELes%20Wexner%20touring%20the%20exhibit%20at%20the%20Wexner%20Center%20for%20the%20Arts%20in%20Columbus%2C%20Ohio.%20Wexner%20says%20he%20is%20%26quot%3Bembarrassed%26quot%3B%20by%20his%20former%20ties%20with%20the%20disgraced%20financier%20Jeffrey%20Epstein%2C%20according%20to%20multiple%20media%20reports.%20%3Cp%3EJay%20LaPrete%2C%20File%2FAssociated%20Press%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%