%3EAttorney%20General%20Letitia%20James%20has%20sued%20the%20NRA%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-nra-is-not-wayne-lapierre-gun-lobby-tells-jury-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eits%20outgoing%20longtime%20leader%20Wayne%20LaPierre%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20three%20other%20veteran%20officers%20of%20the%20gun%20lobby%2C%20alleging%20that%20they%20violated%20state%20not-for-profit%20laws%20for%20years%20by%20squandering%20millions%20of%20dollars%20on%20lavish%20personal%20perks%20and%20gifts%20for%20vendors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20hearing%20Connell's%20objection%2C%20New%20York%20Supreme%20Court%20Justice%20Joel%20Cohen%20gave%20a%20small%2C%20dismissive%20wave%20from%20the%20bench%2C%20and%20allowed%20Rogers%20to%20continue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20didn't%20matter%20that%20I%20had%20taken%20a%20kickboxing%20class%20at%20a%20gym%2C%26quot%3B%20Rogers%20told%20the%20jurors%20of%20the%20attack%20she%20implied%20has%20changed%20her%20mind%20about%20guns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20didn't%20help%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20her%20voice%20wavering%20with%20apparent%20emotion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20everyone%20who%20has%20been%20the%20victim%20of%20a%20crime%20or%20has%20a%20concern%20about%20personal%20safety%20chooses%20to%20have%20a%20gun%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20the%20predominately%20female%20jury.%20The%20jury%20is%20comprised%20of%20eight%20women%20and%20four%20men%20who%20won't%20learn%20if%20they%20are%20jurors%20or%20alternates%20until%20just%20before%20deliberations%2C%20sometime%20in%20mid-February.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20depending%20on%20your%20specific%20situation%2C%20it%20might%20make%20you%20feel%20safer%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20the%20thing%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20your%20choice%20in%20America.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20choice%20to%20own%20a%20firearm%20does%20not%20just%20belong%20to%20the%20king%20or%20the%20militia%20or%20the%20cops%20in%20America%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20yours.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20propriety%20of%20the%20lawyer's%20unusual%20opening%20statement%20finale%20%E2%80%94%20which%20sounded%20as%20if%20it%20were%20ripped%20from%20a%20testimonial%20in%20an%20NRA%20brochure%20%E2%80%94%20was%20raised%20again%20by%20state%20lawyers%20once%20the%20jury%20was%20excused%20for%20a%20break.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConnell%2C%20the%20AG's%20special%20counsel%2C%20rose%20from%20her%20seat%20to%20ask%20the%20judge%20to%20give%20a%20%26quot%3Bcurative%20instruction%26quot%3B%20reminding%20them%20that%20the%20case%20is%20not%20about%20gun%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20jurors%20have%20all%20been%20told%20multiple%20times%20that%20this%20case%20is%20not%20about%20gun%20rights%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20said%2C%20denying%20her%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AG%20alleges%20the%20NRA's%20top%20leadership%20considered%20LaPierre%20to%20be%20its%20%26quot%3Bking%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20allowed%20him%20to%20spend%20millions%20in%20donor%20dollars%20on%20luxury%20travel%2C%20designer%20clothing%2C%20and%20gifts%20for%20favored%20vendors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fighting%20that%20allegation%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20AG's%20demand%20that%20a%20monitor%20be%20installed%20at%20the%20NRA%20to%20fight%20future%20corruption%20%E2%80%94%20Rogers%20further%20used%20Tuesday's%20opening%20statements%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-nra-is-not-wayne-lapierre-gun-lobby-tells-jury-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20portray%20the%20gun%20lobby%20as%20a%20victim%20of%20rogue%20former%20officers%2C%20LaPierre%20included.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20told%20jurors%20that%20LaPierre%20has%20paid%20the%20NRA%20back%20%E2%80%94%20with%20interest%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20fraud-auditing%20software%20and%20other%20safeguards%20are%20now%20in%20place%20to%20prevent%20new%20violations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20seeks%20yet-stated%20monetary%20penal