nt%20lawyers%20once%20made%20the%20exact%20opposite%20argument%20%E2%80%94%20a%20discrepancy%20two%20of%20the%20appellate%20judges%20picked%20up%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpecifically%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewhen%20Trump%20was%20impeached%20over%20the%20Capitol%20riot%20in%202021%2C%20his%20lawyers%20drilled%20down%20on%20one%20key%20point%3A%20a%20former%20president%20shouldn't%20face%20impeachment%20proceedings%3B%20he%20should%20face%20the%20courts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20rationale%20that%20many%20Republicans%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Minority%20Leader%20Mitch%20McConnell%20%E2%80%94%20used%20when%20voting%20to%20acquit%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20criminal%20justice%20system%20in%20this%20country.%20We%20have%20civil%20litigation.%20And%20former%20presidents%20are%20not%20immune%20from%20being%20held%20accountable%20by%20either%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20McConnell%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usnews.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Farticles%2F2021-02-14%2Fread-mcconnell-speech-after-trumps-impeachment-trial-acquittal%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20on%20the%20Senate%20floor%20in%202021%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Trump%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-appeals-hearing-lawyer-argues-president-rival-assassinated-congress-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efacing%20those%20courts%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20criminal%20election%20interference%20case%20brought%20by%20Special%20Counsel%20Jack%20Smith.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20defense%20lawyer%2C%20D.%20John%20Sauer%2C%20argued%20before%20the%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20appeals%20court%20panel%20that%20a%20president%20cannot%20be%20criminally%20prosecuted%20for%20his%20actions%20in%20office%20if%20he%20wasn't%20impeached%20and%20convicted%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20two%20of%20the%20judges%20noted%20that%20Trump%20had%20relied%20on%20the%20opposite%20argument%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20about%20the%20tw