d%20representatives%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20as%20the%20term%20of%20over%2028%2C000%20panchayat%20members%20ended%20today%20with%20no%20fresh%20elections%20in%20sight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20absence%20of%20an%20elected%20government%20in%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20for%20more%20than%20five%20years%2C%20Panchayats-elected%20local%20bodies%20were%20the%20only%20democratic%20institutions%20functional%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20administration%20of%20the%20Union%20Territory%20is%20likely%20to%20appoint%20administrators%20who%20will%20exercise%20the%20powers%20of%20grassroots%20elected%20bodies%20till%20the%20time%20fresh%20elections%20are%20held.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20State%20Election%20Commission%20today%20announced%20a%20revision%20of%20electoral%20rolls%20which%20will%20be%20published%20by%20February%2026.%20It%20will%20be%20followed%20by%20a%20delimitation%20of%20Panchayats%20and%20reservation%20of%20seats%20for%20OBCs%2C%20sources%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20State%20Election%20Commission%20will%20run%20a%20special%20campaign%20to%20undertake%20an%20annual%20summary%20revision%20of%20panchayat%20electoral%20rolls%2C%26quot%3B%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20State%20Election%20Commissioner%2C%20BR%20Sharma%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20District%20Development%20Councils%20(%20DDC)%2C%20which%20is%20the%20third%20tier%20of%20the%20Panchayati%20Raj%20System%20will%20continue%20to%20function%2C%20they%20become%20meaningless%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20panchayats%20and%20block%20development%20councils.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElections%20for%20the%20panchayats%20and%20Urban%20local%20bodies%20were%20last%20held%20in%20November%20and%20December%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20wake%20of%20an%20election%20boycott%20by%20the%20National%20Conference%20and%20the%20PDP%2C%20most%20of%20the%20panchayat%20members%20were%20elected%20unopposed.%20Around%2012%2C000%20seats%20remained%20vacant%20and%20were%20filled%20after%20the%20by-elections%20two%20years%20later%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20completion%20of%20the%20five-year%20term%2C%20all%20the%20urban%20local%20bodies%20ceased%20to%20exist%20in%20December%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJammu%20and%20Kashmir%20has%20been%20under%20direct%20Central%20rule%20since%20June%202018.%20Last%20month%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20set%20the%20deadline%20for%20holding%20assembly%20elections%20before%20September%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704820380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-06%2F9k1e64a8_srinagar-generic-afp_625x300_02_June_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fterm-of-last-elected-body-in-jammu-and-kashmir-ends-no-fresh-elections-in-sight-4831676%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20curtain%20falls%20on%20the%20last%20vestige%20of%20elected%20representatives%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20as%20the%20term%20of%20over%2028%2C000%20panchayat%20members%20ended%20today%20with%20no%20fresh%20elections%20in%20sight.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fterm-of-last-elected-body-in-jammu-and-kashmir-ends-no-fresh-elections-in-sight-4831676%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fterm-of-last-elected-body-in-jammu-and-kashmir-ends-no-fresh-elections-in-sight-4831676%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fterm-of-last-elected-body-in-jammu-and-kashmir-ends-no-fresh-elections-in-sight-4831676%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Spain%20to%20reintroduce%20mandatory%20face%20mask%20wearing%20in%20hospitals%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704819000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F01%2F768x432%2Fskynews-spain-facemask_6416344.jpg%3F20240109163044%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.