%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Twitter%20user%20refused%20to%20back%20down.%20%26quot%3BCulture%20aside.%20Is%20rice%20really%20a%20finger%20food%3F%20Shoving%20grains%20into%20your%20mouth%20with%20saliva%20at%20an%20airport%20is%20appalling.%20At%20least%20with%20a%20French%20fry%2C%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20eat%20the%20portion%20you%20touched.%20You%20wouldn't%20believe%20the%20number%20of%20ppl%20who%20don't%20wash%20their%20hands%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20user%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20her%20mouth%2C%20her%20hands.%20Stop%20interfering%20and%20mind%20your%20business.%20Your%20handle%20name%20and%20your%20actions%20don't%20match%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20a%20fourth%20user%2C%20while%20another%20explained%20why%20anyone%20eating%20their%20food%20with%20their%20hands%20shouldn't%20be%20anybody%20else's%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704814800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F5fet0g3_airport-video_625x300_09_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fvideo-of-woman-eating-rice-with-hands-at-airport-divides-internet-4830750%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20video%20of%20a%20woman%20eating%20rice%20with%20her%20hands%20at%20an%20airport%20has%20surfaced%20online%20and%20prompted%20a%20discussion%20among%20netizens.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fvideo-of-woman-eating-rice-with-hands-at-airport-divides-internet-4830750%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fvideo-of-woman-eating-rice-with-hands-at-airport-divides-internet-4830750%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fvideo-of-woman-eating-rice-with-hands-at-airport-divides-internet-4830750%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Her%20Own%20Words%3A%20What%20Bilkis%20Bano%20Went%20Through%20in%202002%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%2