20or%20decline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20indicators%2C%20such%20as%20thali%20cost%2C%20FMCG%20(%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EFast-moving%20consumer%20goods%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E)%20earnings%2C%20and%20luxury%20goods%20demand%2C%20may%20provide%20a%20more%20comprehensive%20understanding%20of%20how%20different%20segments%20of%20the%20population%20are%20faring.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThali%20cost%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Crisil%2C%20a%20ratings%20agency%2C%20a%20vegetarian%20thali%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Feconomy%2Fveg-thali-became-costlier-food-inflation-likely-to-rise-further-so-is-december-headline-inflation%2Farticle67719355.ece%23%3A~%3Atext%3DA%2520report%2520by%2520CRISIL%2520released%2C%252Dyear%252C%25E2%2580%259D%2520it%2520said.%5C%22%3Ewas%20costlier%3C%2Fa%3E%20yearly%20by%2012%25%20in%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20vegetarian%20thali%20comprises%20roti%2C%20vegetables%20(onion%2C%20tomato%2C%20and%20potato)%2C%20rice%2C%20dal%2C%20curd%2C%20and%20salad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20non-vegetarian%20thali%20includes%20chicken%20instead%20of%20dal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20said%20that%20the%20vegetarian%20thali%20cost%20was%20led%20by%20a%20substantial%20increase%20of%2082%25%20and%2042%25%20in%20the%20prices%20of%20onion%20and%20tomato%2C%20respectively%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Feconomy%2Fveg-thali-became-costlier-food-inflation-likely-to-rise-further-so-is-december-headline-inflation%2Farticle67719355.ece%23%3A~%3Atext%3DA%2520report%2520by%2520CRISIL%2520released%2C%252Dyear%252C%25E2%2580%259D%2520it%2520said.%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3EHindu%20BusinessLine%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPrices%20of%20pulses%2C%20which%20account%20for%209%25%20of%20the%20veg%20thali%20cost%2C%20also%20increased%2024%25%20on-year%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%20However%2C%20the%20non-veg%20thali%20declined%204%25%20on%20a%20yearly%20basis.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20decline%20in%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20non-veg%20thali%20was%20due%20to%20a%2015%25%20decline%20in%20broiler%20prices%20on-year%20amid%20higher%20production%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESwati%20Arora%2C%20economist%20with%20HDFC%20Bank%2C%20told%20the%20business%20daily%20that%20food%20inflation%20is%20expected%20to%20remain%20high%2C%20driven%20by%20higher%20pulses%2C%20cereals%20and%20sugar%20prices%2C%20which%20is%20likely%20to%20exert%20upward%20pressure%20on%20headline%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20weak%20Rabi%20sowing%20progress%20in%20pulses%20is%20also%20a%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20positive%20side%2C%20moderation%20in%20vegetable%20prices%20with%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20winter%20season%20is%20likely%20to%20keep%20the%20upside%20on%20food%20inflation%20in%20check.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalysing%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fcost-of-home-cooked-vegetarian-meal-rises-by-10-non-vegetarian-thali-by-5-report%5C%22%3Emonthly%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffood%2Ftomato-prices-monthly-cost-of-vegetarian-thali-rises-by-34-crisil%5C%22%3Eand%20yearly%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fis-india-facing-thali-trouble-again%5C%22%3Ecost%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20a%20standard%20thali%20could%20provide%20insights%20into%20the%20affordability%20of%20basic%20necessities%20for%20the%20general%20population.%20A%20rising%20thali%20cost%20could%20indicate%20inflationary%20pressures%20impacting%20the%20affordability%20of%20essential%20food%20items%20for%20certain%20income%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fmodi-amrit-kaal-hunger-unemployment%5C%22%3EHunger%20and%20Unemployment%20in%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Amrit%20Kaal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELuxury%20sales%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20largest%20realtor%20DLF%20on%20January%208%20said%20that%20it%20sold%20entire%201%2C113%20luxury%20flats%20in%20a%20project%20(DLF%20Parivana%20South)%20in%20Gurugram%20for%20Rs%207%2C200%20crore%20within%20three%20days%20of%20pre-launch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20top%20luxury%20car%20brand%20Mercedes-Benz%20said%20that%202023%20was%20its%20best%20year%20in%20the%20India%20market%2C%20as%20it%20sold%2017%2C408%20four-wheelers%20in%202023%2C%20up%2010%25%20year%20on%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAudi%20India%20announced%20that%20its%20sales%20in%202023%20grew%20by%2090%25%20to%207%2C931%20units.%20In%20the%20coming%20days%2C%20BMW%20and%20other%20luxury%20players%20in%20this%20niche%20segment%20are%20also%20expected%20to%20report%20record%20sales%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fbusiness%2F2024%2Fjan%2F09%2Fultra-expensive-homes-luxury-cars-witness-record-sales-2649365.html%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3ENew%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20comparison%2C%20the%20affordable%20and%20low-cost%20housing%20segment%20has%20witnessed%20a%20decline%20in%20volume%20in%202023.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fbusiness%2Fwhy-is-indias-affordable-housing-market-shrinking%2Farticle67372484.ece%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20demand%20for%20affordable%20housing%20has%20declined%20due%20to%20high%20taxes%2C%20rising%20land%20costs%2C%20and%20increased%20home%20loan%20interest%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20defines%20affordable%20housing%20as%20residential%20units%20that%20are%2060%20square%20metres%20at%2C%20or%20under%20Rs%2045%20lakhs%20in%20%E2%80%9Cmetro%20areas%E2%80%9D.%20Metro%20areas%20are%20Mumbai%2C%20Delhi%20National%20Capital%20Region%20(NCR)%2C%20Chennai%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20Hyderabad%2C%20Kolkata%2C%20Kochi%2C%20Pune%20and%20Ahmedabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevelopers%20told%20the%20daily%20that%20sharp%20rises%20in%20land%20value%2C%20direct%20and%20indirect%20taxes%2C%20as%20well%20as%20escalating%20costs%20of%20construction%20materials%20and%20other%20inputs%2C%20have%20resulted%20in%20their%20incapacity%20to%20deliver%20affordable%20housing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20result%2C%20almost%20none%20of%20the%20projects%20in%20the%20metros%20can%20take%20the%20benefit%20of%20provisions%20of%20affordable%20housing%20such%20as%20Section%2080IBA%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kapil%20Gandhi%2C%20managing%20director%2C%20Sigma%20One%20Universal%2C%20a%20Pune-brd%20real%20estate%20company%2C%20told%20the%20daily.%20%E2%80%9COf%20every%20Rs%20100%20invested%20in%20real%20estate%2C%2035%25%20to%2045%25%20goes%20directly%20to%20the%20government%2C%20which%20includes%20heavy%20premiums%2C%20direct%20and%20indirect%20taxes%2C%20and%20GST.%20Sometimes%20these%20do%20not%20come%20with%20a%20set-off%20and%20other%20costs.%20So%20a%20good%20property%20can%20not%20cost%20less%20than%20Rs%2065-75%20lakh%20in%20any%20metro%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fvideo-santosh-mehrotra-unemployment-unpaid-worker%5C%22%3E%3Cins%3EWatch%3A%20What%20India%E2%80%99s%20Growing%20Army%20of%20Unpaid%20Workers%20Means%20for%20It%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFMCG%20earnings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFMCG%20companies%20saw%20a%20subdued%20growth%20in%20overall%20revenues%20during%20the%20July-September%20quarter%20of%20FY24.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.financialexpress.com%2Fbusiness%2Findustry-consumer-goods-sector-q2-performance-muted-demand-sales-growth-impacted-due-to-delayed-festive-season-price-hikes-3314323%2F%5C%22%3Ebrokerage%20firms%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20impact%20on%20sales%20growth%20of%20the%20sector%20during%20the%20period%20was%20largely%20due%20to%20the%20delayed%20festive%20season%20and%20from%20the%20price-hike%20anniversarisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CReported%20earning%20growth%20remained%20strong%20in%20Q2%2C%20albeit%20this%20was%20largely%20led%20by%20margin%20expansion%20off%20a%20low%20base.%20Demand%20trends%20remain%20sluggish%2C%20which%20is%20further%20exacerbated%20by%20increase%20in%20competitive%20pressures%20especially%20from%20smaller%20players%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Jefferies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.financialexpress.com%2Fbusiness%2Findustry-consumer-goods-sector-q2-performance-muted-demand-sales-growth-impacted-due-to-delayed-festive-season-price-hikes-3314323%2F%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%3Cem%3E%20Financial%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20Q2%20earnings%20were%20a%20mirror%20image%20of%20the%20Q1FY24%20performance.%20This%20is%20because%20growth%20was%20largely%20driven%20by%20margin%20expansion%2C%20while%20revenue%20growth%20stood%20in%20low%20single%20digits%20due%20to%20muted%20volume%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%2C%20%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Standard%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fmore-inventory-days-for-consumer-goods-as-low-demand-causes-supply-chain-congestion%5C%22%3Ehad%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20persistent%20low%20demand%20in%20the%20FMCG%20sector%20is%20causing%20supply%20chain%20congestion%2C%20leading%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20inventory%20days%2C%20with%20stocks%20accumulating%20at%20distributors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20distributor%20told%20the%20business%20daily%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cfestival%20season%20demand%20did%20not%20offer%20any%20respite%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20summer%20wedding%20season%20remained%20weak%2C%20causing%20a%20build-up%20in%20inventory%20for%20the%20past%20few%20months.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704808814000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F09163250%2Fimage-1707.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Frising-thali-cost-m