3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106667265.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ETaiwan's%20closely-watched%20election%20on%20Saturday%20is%20described%20by%20Chinese%20officials%20as%20a%20choice%20between%20war%20and%20peace.%20Frontrunner%20candidate%20Lai%20Ching-te%2C%20who%20Beijing%20calls%20a%20stubborn%20worker%20for%20Taiwan%20independence%2C%20is%20drawing%20ire.%20Beijing%20claims%20Taiwan%20as%20part%20of%20its%20territory%20and%20has%20vowed%20to%20seize%20the%20island%20for%20unification.%20China's%20options%20for%20attacking%20Taiwan%20include%20decapitation%20strikes%2C%20blockade%2C%20and%20amphibious%20landing.%20Beijing%20is%20already%20tightening%20its%20squeeze%20on%20Taiwan%2C%20and%20there%20are%20concerns%20of%20a%20major%20cyberattack%20on%20the%20island's%20key%20infrastructure.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fpossible-scenarios-for-a-chinese-invasion-of-taiwan%2Farticleshow%2F106667265.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fpossible-scenarios-for-a-chinese-invasion-of-taiwan%2Famp_articleshow%2F106667265.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fpossible-scenarios-for-a-chinese-invasion-of-taiwan%2Famp_articleshow%2F106667265.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Isn't%20Time%20for%20Confusion%2C%20Opposition%20Should%20Use%20Their%20January%2022%20Ayodhya%20Invitations%20Well%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2F21170011%2F1_Ayodhya_Ram_Paidi_Uttar_Pradesh_India_2013.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20January%2022%2C%20just%20months%20before%20a%20general%20election%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20is%20going%20back%20to%20the%20holy%20town%20of%20Ayodhya%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20In%20doing%20so%2C%20it%20is%20sewing%20together%20politics%20and%20religion%20with%20impunity.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20opposition%20parties%20are%20still%20deciding%20as%20to%20whether%20to%20attend%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20ceremony%2C%20which%20is%20clearly%20designed%20to%20give%20pole%20position%20to%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20the%20party.%20They%20would%20do%20well%20to%20recall%20how%20religion%20has%20been%20used%20since%20the%201990s%20by%20the%20BJP%20to%20register%20significant%20electoral%20progress.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Latching%20on%20to%20a%20runaway%20%3Cem%3Erath%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20never%20helped%20the%20opposition.%20Crafting%20and%20standing%20by%20an%20alternate%20and%20confident%20theme%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20has.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%201991%20general%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20became%20the%20second%20largest%20entity%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20This%20was%20an%20impressive%20upward%20curve%20for%20the%20party%2C%20considering%20the%20fact%20that%20in%201984%20when%20it%20had%20contested%20the%20parliamentary%20elections%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20it%20could%20grab%20only%20two%20seats.%20This%20was%2C%20of%20course%2C%20much%20less%20than%20what%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20predecessor%2C%20the%20Jana%20Sangh%20had%20got%20before%20it%20became%20the%20Janata%20Party.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%201991%20general%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20could%20not%20only%20reap%20a%20rich%20electoral%20harvest%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20which%20has%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20largest%20number%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20but%20the%20party%20also%20saw%20its%20vote%20share%20shoot%20up%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20including%20southern%20India.%20From%207.4%25%20in%201984%2C%20and%2011.4%25%20in%201989%2C%20it%20surged%20to%2020.1%25%20in%201991%2C%20which%20eventually%20cleared%20the%20path%20for%20the%20Hindutva%20party%20to%20become%20the%20single%20largest%20in%20the%20next%20general%20elections%20in%201996.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20year%20later%2C%20in%201997%2C%20the%20party%20could%20return%20to%20power%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20This%20was%20followed%20by%20it%20winning%20more%20seats%20in%20the%20assemblies%20of%20some%20other%20Hindi%20heartland%20states.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20373px)%2085vw%2C%20373px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2F15133951%2Fmodi-advani.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Narendra%20Modi%20with%20L.K.%20Advani%20during%20Advani's%20rath%20yatra.%20Credit%3A%20Twitter%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22373%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2F15133951%2Fmodi-advani.jpg%20454w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2F15133951%2Fmodi-advani-300x272.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-205233%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22338%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ENarendra%20Modi%20with%20L.K.%20Advani%20during%20Advani%E2%80%99s%20rath%20yatra.%20Credit%3A%20Twitter%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20single%20most%20important%20reason%20for%20that%20firm%20and%20steady%20rise%20is%20widely%20considered%20to%20be%20the%20L.K.%20Advani-led%20Rath%20Yatra%20to%20Ayodhya%20in%201990%20%E2%80%93%20where%20he%20rode%20a%20Toyota-rath%20on%20the%20strident%20demand%20to%20build%20a%20Ram%20temple%20where%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20stood.%20It%20was%20a%20response%20to%20the%20Mandal%20report%20being%20accepted%20by%20the%20V.P.%20Singh%20government%20which%20threw%20a%20spanner%20in%20the%20works%20of%20the%20BJP%20which%20had%20until%20then%20been%20supporting%20the%20government.%20Kalyan%20Singh%20could%20successfully%20fashion%20a%20victory%20around%20that%20strong%20Hindu%20sentiment%20for%20a%20Ram%20Mandir%20at%20Ayodhya%20and%20formed%20a%20government%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20January%2022%2C%20when%20Narendra%20Modi%20will%20virtually%20don%20the%20role%20of%20a%20priest%20at%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20the%20temple%20at%20Ayodhya%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20no%20stone%20would%20be%20left%20unturned%20in%20trying%20to%20re-run%20the%20old%20theme%2C%20and%20use%20the%20ceremony%20to%20be%20able%20to%20win%20another%20general%20election.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOpposition%E2%80%99s%20false%20dilemma%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ceremony%20is%20also%20being%20weaponised%20to%20checkmate%20the%20opposition%20which%20is%20threatening%20to%20contest%20the%202024%20elections%20unitedly%20against%20the%20BJP.%20Accordingly%2C%20invitations%20have%20been%20dispatched%20to%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20top%20leaders%20like%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20party%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20CPI%20(M)%20general%20secretary%20Sitaram%20Yechury%2C%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20leader%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20while%20also%20steering%20clear%20of%20the%20likes%20of%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20%E2%80%93%20lest%20his%20faction%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20draw%20any%20traction%20electorally%20in%20Maharashtra%20from%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInvited%20formally%20or%20not%2C%20January%2022%20has%20put%20several%20opposition%20leaders%20in%20a%20bind%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20or%20not%20to%20join%20the%20ceremony%20led%20by%20the%20ruling%20party.%20Their%20dilemma%20essentially%20springs%20out%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Ram%20temple%20issue%20has%20an%20undeniable%20link%20to%20the%20religious%20sentiments%20of%20millions%20of%20believing%20Hindus.%20Whether%20they%20show%20up%20at%20the%20January%2022%20ceremony%20or%20not%2C%20here%20are%20two%20arguments%20they%20must%20be%20able%20to%20present%20to%20the%20voters%20to%20be%20able%20to%20cut%20through%20the%20trap%20they%20find%20themselves%20in.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ERam%20is%20above%20politics%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20the%20January%2022%20ceremony%20will%20be%20led%20not%20by%20any%20Hindu%20religious%20leader%20but%20by%20Modi%2C%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20only%20face%2C%20gives%20the%20game%20away.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patrika.com%2Fayodhya-news%2Fram-mandir-inauguration-puri-shankaracharya-not-go-ayodhya-comment-on-pm-modi-8665759%2F%5C%22%3EShankaracharya%20has%20already%20said%20it%3C%2Fa%3E.%20To%20go%20to%20the%202024%20general%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20needs%20a%20pan-India%20narrative%20to%20surmount%20a%2010-year%20incumbency%20load%20%E2%80%93%20one%20which%20is%20much%20more%20emotive%20than%20Kashmir%20or%20Pakistan%20bogeys%2C%20and%20this%20is%20particularly%20true%20for%20southern%20and%20eastern%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20significant%20that%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20trusted%20aide%20and%20former%20principal%20secretary%20at%20the%20PMO%2C%20Nripendra%20Mishra%2C%20was%20placed%20at%20Ayodhya%20to%20head%20the%20temple%20construction%20committee%20of%20the%20Ram%20Janambhoomi%20Teerth%20Kshetra.%20That%20project%20under%20Mishra%20is%20set%20to%20plant%20Modi%20this%20January%2022%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20Hriday%20Samrat%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20then%20the%20opposition%20leaders%20must%20be%20able%20to%20hold%20up%20to%20their%20voters%20is%20a%20simple%20but%20assertive%20line%20that%20the%20deity%2C%20Ram%2C%20is%20above%20politics.%20They%20must%20say%20that%20people%E2%80%99s%20religious%20sentiments%20must%20not%20be%20permitted%20to%20become%20a%20tool%20for%20a%20political%20party%20which%20is%20desperate%20to%20win%20an%20election.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20being%20an%20ardent%20Hindu%2C%20a%20believer%20of%20Ram%2C%20is%20different%20from%20being%20a%20BJP%20voter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F23120832%2Fl7l9chag_ram-temple-proposed-design-august-2020_625x300_04_August_20.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22650%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F23120832%2Fl7l9chag_ram-temple-proposed-design-august-2020_625x300_04_August_20.jpg%20650w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F23120832%2Fl7l9chag_ram-temple-proposed-design-august-2020_625x300_04_August_20-300x185.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-629759%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20design%20for%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20vote%20for%20any%20party%20in%20an%20election%2C%20a%20conscious%20citizen%20must%20ask%20questions%20that%20affect%20the%20quality%20of%20her%20day-to-day%20life.%20So%2C%20before%20the%202024%20general%20elections%2C%20too%2C%20voters%20must%20ask%20the%20Modi%20government%3A%20What%20has%20it%20done%20to%20create%20employment%20opportunities%2C%20to%20control%20price%20rise%2C%20to%20make%20healthcare%20and%20education%20accessible%2C%20and%20to%20ensure%20our%20borders%20are%20safe%20and%20secure%3F%20The%20Ram%20temple%20is%20being%20constructed%20due%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fayodhya-verdict-supreme-court-judgment%5C%22%3Efavourable%20judgment%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20the%20opposition%20could%20do%20well%20to%20remind%20voters%20of%20this.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPerhaps%20on%20January%2022%2C%20it%20would%20also%20be%20worthwhile%20for%20opposition%20leaders%20to%20remind%20all%20conscious%20citizens%20of%20the%20country%20about%20the%20father%20of%20the%20nation%2C%20Mahatma%20Gandhi.%20While%20falling%20to%20the%20bullets%20pumped%20into%20his%20frail%20body%20by%20a%20fanatic%20during%20a%20prayer%20meeting%2C%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20last%20words%20were%2C%20%E2%80%98Hey%20Ram%E2%80%99.%20That%20utterance%20should%20signify%20how%20much%20of%20an%20ardent%20Ram%20worshipper%20he%20was%2C%20perhaps%20different%20from%20the%20one%20who%20took%20his%20life%2C%20a%20former%20member%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%2C%20the%20ideological%20fount%20of%20the%20BJP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20democracy%2C%20stupid%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20January%2022%2C%20opposition%20leaders%20must%20be%20able%20to%20convey%20to%20the%20voters%20that%20if%20they%20attend%20the%20ceremony%2C%20they%20would%20only%20be%20standing%20behind%20a%20BJP%20leader%20who%20would%20be%20using%20all%20possible%20media%20under%20his%20command%20(and%20there%20are%20very%20few%20honourable%20exceptions%20left)%20to%20launch%20a%20grand%20campaign%20for%20his%20party%20to%20be%20able%20to%20win%20a%20crucial%20election.%20The%20party%20and%20its%20main%20mascot%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fayodhya-rss-bjp-vhp-ram-temple%5C%22%3Ebrazenly%20hoping%20to%20milk%20religious%20sentiments%20for%20votes.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbove%20all%2C%20non-BJP%20leaders%20should%20be%20able%20to%20remind%20all%20patriotic%20citizens%20of%20the%20country%20that%20it%20is%20the%20citizen%20who%20is%20the%20sovereign%2C%20and%20proud%20custodians%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20democracy.%20That%20acknowledgment%20comes%20with%20the%20fact%20that%20a%20democracy%20is%20run%20by%20a%20constitution%3B%20and%2C%20that%20no%20constitution%20in%20any%20democracy%2C%20including%20ours%2C%20mandates%20the%20prime%20minister%20to%20be%20a%20monarch%20or%20a%20priest.%20We%20are%20not%20a%20constitutional%20monarchy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECountries%20often%20require%20moments%20of%20clarity%20like%20this%20one.%20This%20may%20well%20be%20one%20where%20the%20courage%20to%20call%20it%20what%20it%20is%20decides%20the%20shape%20of%20the%20years%20to%20come.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704796258000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2F21170011%2F1_Ayodhya_Ram_Paidi_Uttar_Pradesh_India_2013.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fayodhya-january-22-modi-opposition%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22They%20will%20be%20rewarded%20for%20courage%20and%20ability%20to%20call%20out%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20aim%20of%20politicising%20religion.%20Lining%20up%20behind%20as%20Modi%20as%20he%20behaves%20as%20'yajman'%20won%E2%80%99t%20win%20them%20votes%2C%20but%20will%20be%20a%20mockery%20of%20the%20country%20as%20a%20whole.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A30%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fayodhya-january-22-modi-opposition%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Germany%E2%80%99s%20World%20Cup-Winning%20Player%2C%20Coach%20Franz%20Beckenbauer%20Passes%20Away%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F09152605%2FCmvy8BWXgAA0-TG.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EFranz%20Anton%20Beckenbauer%20believed%20in%20reincarnation.%20%E2%80%9CMaybe%20I%E2%80%99ve%20been%20here%20once%20before%2C%20as%20a%20plant%20or%20something%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20a%20Berlin%20newspaper%20in%201994.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20not%20been%20able%20to%20transport%20myself%20back%20yet%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20something%20I%E2%80%99d%20like%20to%20do.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWho%20knows%20how%20many%20lives%20Beckenbauer%20had%20already%20lived%2C%20