%26nbsp%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F09152825%2FUntitled-design-3-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20as%20a%20nation%20are%20a%20bit%20relieved%2C%20finally.%20After%20some%20back%20to%20back%20judicial%20reverses%20where%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20top%20court%20seemed%20to%20have%20failed%20to%20stand%20up%20for%20us%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fbilkis-bano-supreme-court-gujarat-not-competent-remission%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%20made%20some%20amends%20yesterday%20by%20ordering%20that%20the%20rapists%20of%20Bilkis%20Bano%20surrender%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20go%20back%20to%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20any%20requiem%20for%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20need%20not%20be%20written%20yet%20is%20a%20huge%20relief.%20In%20sending%20back%20the%20rapists%20where%20they%20rightly%20belong%2C%20the%20top%20court%20has%20once%20again%20restored%20in%20us%20some%20hope%20that%20we%20need%20to%20celebrate%20in%20these%20challenging%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20more%20ways%20than%20one%2C%20Monday%E2%80%99s%20ruling%20would%20qualify%20as%20a%20rousing%20one%20%E2%80%93%20if%20one%20is%20permitted%20to%20say%20so%20in%20legalese.%20Apart%20from%20reversing%20what%20was%20a%20grotesque%20abuse%20of%20power%20that%20saw%20the%20rapists%20being%20let%20off%20prematurely%2C%20it%20tore%20into%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20that%20perpetuated%20the%20hair-raising%20abuse%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20held%20guilty%20of%20fraud%20and%20complicity%20by%20the%20learned%20judges%20is%20certainly%20a%20blot%20on%20our%20famed%20Gujarat%20Model%20of%20governance.%C2%A0%20And%20if%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20has%20any%20shame%2C%20it%20should%20be%20very%20deeply%20ashamed%20after%20what%20the%20judges%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20hold%20on.%20Have%20you%20seen%20any%20contrition%20on%20the%20part%20of%20anyone%20responsible%20for%20this%20abuse%20yet%3F%20Has%20anyone%20owned%20up%20any%20responsibility%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%2C%20I%20am%20being%20too%20demanding.%20After%20all%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20just%20been%20a%20day%20since%20the%20scathing%20ruling%20was%20delivered%20and%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20cleaners.%20May%20be%2C%20we%20need%20to%20be%20more%20patient%20and%20await%20some%20shame%20to%20kick%20in%20among%20at%20least%C2%A0%20some%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20signs%20in%20the%20first%2024%20hours%20are%20rather%20ominous%2C%20leaving%20little%20room%20for%20any%20optimism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20we%20rejoice%20and%20hail%20the%20judgment%2C%20the%20ecosystem%20that%20aids%20and%20abets%20the%20establishment%20that%20from%20time%20to%20time%20shocks%20us%20by%20its%20recurrent%20overreach%20has%20gone%20silent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20has%20not%20spoken.%20The%20home%20minister%20too%20has%20not%20spoken.%20None%20has%20heard%20the%20Gujarat%20chief%20minister%20say%20anything%20on%20the%20denouement.%20For%20that%20matter%2C%20none%20who%20matters%20in%20Gujarat%20have%20said%20anything%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ftoday-i-can-breathe-again-says-bilkis-bano-after-landmark-supreme-court-judgement%5C%22%3EToday%2C%20I%20Can%20Breathe%20Again%2C%20Says%20Bilkis%20Bano%20After%20Landmark%20Supreme%20Court%20Judgement%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20outrage%20that%20we%20felt%20at%20the%20remission%20of%20the%20sentences%20for%20the%20rapists%20and%20the%20relief%20that%20we%20are%20currently%20bathing%20in%20following%20its%20reversal%20do%20not%20seem%20to%20be%20shared%20by%20one%20and%20all.%20Last%20night%E2%80%99s%20prime%20time%20television%20shows%20offered%20us%20a%20glimpse%20of%20the%20lack%20of%20excitement%20on%20the%20part%20of%20many.%20Barring%20a%20few%2C%20most%20anchors%20were%20busy%20outraging%20over%20Maldives