of%20humanity%20and%20equality%20at%20a%20time%20these%20are%20becoming%20rare%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20newspaper%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20of%20Justices%20B.V.%20Nagarathna%20and%20Ujjal%20Bhuyan%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-bilkis-bano-state-of-gujarat-remission-convict-246114%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20state%20of%20Gujarat%20%E2%80%9Cacted%20in%20complicity%20with%20the%20convicts%E2%80%9D.%20The%20top%20court%20said%20that%20the%20state%20government%20%E2%80%9Cacted%20in%20tandem%E2%80%9D%20with%20convict%20and%20breached%20the%20rule%20of%20law%2C%20usurped%20power%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-artid%3D%5C%2267719957%5C%22%20data-title%3D%5C%22Unlawful%20remission%3A%20On%20the%20Bilkis%20Bano%20case%20%5C%22%20data-url%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fopinion%2Feditorial%2Funlawful-remission-the-hindu-editorial-on-the-bilkis-bano-case%2Farticle67719957.ece%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-articleid%3D%5C%2267719957%5C%22%3EThe%20top%20court%E2%80%99s%20verdict%20quashing%20the%20orders%20releasing%2011%20men%20convicted%20for%20the%20heinous%20gang-rape%20and%20murder%20of%20several%20members%20of%20Bano%E2%80%99s%20family%20during%20the%20Gujarat%20pogrom%20in%202002%20is%20an%20%E2%80%9Cunequivocal%20indictment%20of%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fopinion%2Feditorial%2Funlawful-remission-the-hindu-editorial-on-the-bilkis-bano-case%2Farticle67719957.ece%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20said%20in%20its%20editorial.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-articleid%3D%5C%2267719957%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20ruling%20represents%20a%20blow%20for%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20and%20the%20restoration%20of%20faith%20in%20the%20judiciary%20at%20a%20time%20when%20there%20are%20doubts%20about%20the%20institution%E2%80%99s%20capacity%