5BJanuary%208%2C%202023%5D%20order%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20the%20remission%20was%20obtained%20through%20%E2%80%98fraud%E2%80%99.%20Clearly%2C%20due%20diligence%20was%20compromised%20by%20the%20government%20and%20the%20previous%20bench%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20itself.%20Remissions%20are%20not%20unusual%20in%20the%20case%20of%20life%20convicts%2C%20but%20they%20are%20rarely%20(if%20ever)%20extended%20to%20people%20convicted%20of%20heinous%20crimes%20such%20as%20murder%20and%20rape%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-articleid%3D%5C%2267719957%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CBano%20and%20her%20family%20have%20been%20brave%20and%20relentless%20in%20pursuing%20justice%20%E2%80%93%20twice%20over.%20That%20should%20stay.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-articleid%3D%5C%2267719957%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-articleid%3D%5C%2267719957%5C%22%3ESaying%20that%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20need%20for%20policy%20safeguards%20in%20all%20cases%2C%20%3Cem%3ETOI%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20in%20its%20editorial%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fblogs%2Ftoi-editorials%2Fback-to-jail-sc-judgment-on-remission-in-bilkis-case-underlines-need-for-policy-safeguards-in-all-cases%2F%5C%22%3Enoted%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CRemission%20is%20integral%20to%20the%20justice%20system.%20But%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20ensure%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20a%20matter%20of%20political%20convenience.%20When%20SC%20concluded%20that%20Gujarat%20government%20usurped%20powers%20to%20order%20remission%2C%20the%20risks%20of%20the%20justice%20system%20being%20undermined%20by%20it%20were%20highlighted.%20Justice%20is%20poorly%20served%20not%20just%20by%20arbitrary%20detention%2C%20but%20also%20dubious%20remissions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-articleid%3D%5C%2267719957%5C%22%3EIt%20said%20that%20this%20remission%20was%20%E2%80%9Ccontroversial%20on%20account%20of%20the%20horrific%